                    <h1 style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 10px 0; color: #141312;">Garlic & Oil Pasta Blueprint</h1>
                    <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.1rem;">The ultimate kitchen efficiency showcase. Derived from the classic Spaghetti Aglio e Olio, this strategy relies completely on high-emulsion starchy water and low-cost lipid extraction from fresh garlic to create a slick, glossy coating without using luxury ingredients.</p>

                    <h2 style="font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; margin-top: 40px; color: #141312;">1. Component Unit Ledger</h2>
                    <table class="audit-table">
